  • Constructor Details

    • Television

      public Television(String make, String model, boolean smart, int screenSize, int resolution)
      The EVC that sets the class level variables to the values passed in
      Parameters:
      make - Representing the television make (LG/Samsung/etc)
      model - Representing the television model
      smart - Representing the television is a smart TV
      screenSize - Representing the television screen size
      resolution - Representing the resolution of the television
      Throws:
      IllegalArgumentException - if the strings are null or empty or the screen size is less than 32 or the resolution is less than 720
      NOTE: You must use this. before all class level variables
      NOTE: All paramaters will be passed as final
      NOTE: If resolution is 2160 the TV is 4K
